# Quantumult X - HK Finance Apps DIRECT
# Raw:
# https://raw.githubusercontent.com/niyangup/ios_script_rule/main/hk-finance-direct.list
#
# Quantumult X [filter_remote]:
# https://raw.githubusercontent.com/niyangup/ios_script_rule/main/hk-finance-direct.list, tag=HK Finance Direct, force-policy=DIRECT, enabled=true
#
# 金融 App 不建议开启 MitM；如果仍走代理，在 Quantumult X 请求记录里补 HOST-SUFFIX。

# --- ZA Bank / 众安银行 ---
HOST-SUFFIX,za.group,DIRECT
HOST-SUFFIX,zabank.com.hk,DIRECT
HOST-SUFFIX,zaintl.com,DIRECT
HOST-SUFFIX,zaapi.com,DIRECT
HOST-KEYWORD,zabank,DIRECT
HOST-KEYWORD,za-bank,DIRECT
HOST-KEYWORD,zaintl,DIRECT

